docs.text: Welcome to FedImpute FedImpute is a benchmarking and evaluation tool to assess the effectiveness of federated imputation across various missing data scenarios. What is Missing Data Under Federated Data Scenario? Installation Install python >= 3.8.0 python -m venv ./venv # window gitbash source ./venv/Scripts/activate # linux/unix source ./venv/bin/activate Install the required packages pip install -r requirements.txt
